ActInternational Development Research Centre Act
PrecisAppointment of ANDRÉS ROZENTAL of Mexico City, Mexico, to be a governor of the Board of Governors of the International Development Research Centre, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective March 9, 2007, in the place of Octavio Gomez-Dantés.
